questions.quote: I was wearing that sweater in the coffee shop when Barry came in.
Really? You should be ashamed of yourself. I want you out of here!  How ya' doing?
look come on, let me use it, 5 minutes, I'll pay you back huh?
Look, you're a nice guy, it's just that... we don't have anything in common.
I know. And now they want me to bottle it up. It makes me so mad!
No-one's ever been impeached before. I couldn't live here. We'd have to move to Boca.
Oh, please don't tell me you love me again, Jerry, I can't handle it.
Thank you very much, that's great- >click< Oh! Hold on a sec, I got a call on the other line. >click click< Hello?
Wait, as a matter of fact, wasn't there some guy in your building that you said you liked? He lived up on the fifth floor or something.
Alright listen to me, I got a great idea. Now, you're a heavy sleeper, right? Why don't we just switch apartments?
